        {
            "title": "港股升665後急回  升幅曾收窄至15點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股尾段急速向下，恒生指數低見21872，升幅收窄至15點或0.07%，午後最多曾升665點，見22523點4個月高，現報21990，升132點或0.61%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數曾34點或0.64%，現跌3點或0.06%，報5278點 ; 恒生國企指數升7點或0.1%，報8065點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)升幅收窄至3.34%，報116.9元 ; 阿里健康(00241)升幅收窄至5.46%，報4.64元。 百度(09888)升6.3%，報94.5元。  快手(01024)升7.49%，報50.25元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中芯(00981)倒跌2.92%，報46.55元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14703582-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%87665%e5%be%8c%e6%80%a5%e5%9b%9e-%e5%8d%87%e5%b9%85%e6%9b%be%e6%94%b6%e7%aa%84%e8%87%b315%e9%bb%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-web_HKStock-3.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-13 15:35:23",
